nodes.text: Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection 15

The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection 15 is the fifteenth issue of the fortnightly magazine by De Agostini. Like all issues, it includes a die-cast collectible model and is an officially licensed source of Star Wars information, under Lucas Licensing and the LucasBooks imprint.
